title: Work on $18m Kangaroo Island airport upgrade must begin before airline agreement secured says council
text: The Kangaroo Island Council has acknowledged there is an element of risk in upgrading the island's airport without a potential air service provider confirmed but says it is in talks with two potential airlines. ...
